      "Read machine-package-driven assembly instructions"
    ],
    "recommendedMode": "guided",
    "entryAssemblyIds": [
      "assembly_frame_corner"
    ],
    "prerequisiteNotes": [
      "Learner should understand the difference between a plate, bracket, and fastener."
